0Z","msg":"旺角街市附近間文記 8蚊一杯"},{"pid":"c5644e893619104e6d296d7d27e0902dba256fdb","tid":537894,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"90d996fb3646d3c3be3faed530d5a3ba97ecb1b2","tid":537894,"uid":123112,"like":40,"dislike":40,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T09:04:57.000Z","msg":"台式奶茶 成本好低者, 奶精+阿薩姆茶, 高成本極都係2蚊<br />\n至於珍珠既成本低到唔想講<br />\n<br />\n不過賣咁貴都係人工同租金者<br />\n<br />\n利申: 大陸開左間飲品店"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T15:35:37.000Z","msg":"連登仔邊識計租同人工落成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7574731f894d9106f04c3dd6c137ea89c6f6e425","tid":537894,"uid":90045,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"147e7ba21ff4ef223f63bf438e36276a6cf42783","tid":537894,"uid":9142,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T12:33:47.000Z","msg":"以前大把屋邨/住宅士多仔自己整賣$6一杯啦，成班小學雞淨係識貢茶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T15:53:13.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />6-7年前 屋村餐廳仔搶學生客 十幾蚊個飯加杯5-6蚊珍珠奶茶<br />\n<br />\n唔講加錢轉特飲  好記得貢茶comebuy初出<br />\n鬥得好勁  12蚊中杯 14蚊大杯  而旺角啲生果鋪<br />\n（賣埋椰奶 芒果沙冰嗰幾間）珍珠奶茶先7-8蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4c3c162f1128fb9ffec5618fe1da861d2902bd","tid":537894,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4537890390dfd4d0b5ea43e451e2ecc8c53953a1","tid":537894,"uid":48157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f76e6d39d78b23d78d297379cedf8c7116bddd68","tid":537894,"uid":2020,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T14:07:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>95 97年代,乜唔係靠仙跡岩先有得飲,仲要廿幾蚊杯咩?</blockquote>當年未有貢茶<br />\n旺角5蚊杯之嘛</blockquote>廿年前唔係得仙跡岩有喳咩?</blockquote>杯嘢有秘方呀?<br />\n得佢先識沖?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講緊廿年前呀<br />\n<br />\n廿年前香港人連珍珠奶茶都未必個個知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T14:20:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T15:53:56.000Z","msg":"一見到快可立就即係諗起瘋狂搖搖杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64368e845cdef9ec9507d524cc73d180d0069ecc","tid":537894,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ba5b3b1425b4eb51b7cb5f2e07402bd91a0dbc1","tid":537894,"uid":38188,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T13:47:57.000Z","msg":"10年左右台灣嘅品牌係香港就賣緊$10左右(大卡司果啲)<br />\n但一啲小食舖賣果啲細size珍珠奶茶就$5-$7一杯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T15:54:48.000Z","msg":"士多奶茶味同依家差唔多<br />\n唯一唔好係甜 同埋珍珠軟囉  但好撚抵"},{"pid":"0661f010b819fd52ad139ded896255af83b85b83","tid":537894,"uid":74302,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"fed92ba213a88f6a0281a010c27bc5dc5f91700b","tid":537894,"uid":34489,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"650b9f8b4fa50f3089e62b1877be5743d79d7e47","tid":537894,"uid":16061,"like":144,"dislike":3,"score":141,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T06:36:54.000Z","msg":"4 5蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T06:47:35.000Z","msg":"街邊d小食店好多都有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T15:57:18.000Z","msg":"十年前。旺角街邊小袋鋪都有<br />\n我記得係6蚊杯<br />\n當然質素麻麻<br />\n而家諗番都唔知多唔多大腸桿菌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後來興日出茶太，未爆台灣塑化劑風波前。12-14蚊一杯左右<br />\n<br />\n之後一直都係十幾蚊杯<br />\n直到有左天仁茗茶。我先第一次飲廿蚊既一杯奶綠。但好飲 都覺得值<br />\n<br />\n而家咩茶湯會，鹿角<br />\n都係廿尾一杯野<br />\n癡線....鹿果間係好飲<br />\n但份量少。又排長龍 又貴<br />\n所以香港人接受能力係好高....<br />\n我都係飲番天仁算"},{"pid":"e158dcaadd905588c85101e19f8b2ca09ebb2f45","tid":537894,"uid":90045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"46dfd23a21a0a042033f334309f444c778e6ac21","tid":537894,"uid":136988,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4537890390dfd4d0b5ea43e451e2ecc8c53953a1","tid":537894,"uid":481