" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F000653_111677c53f23e6dc3863152e0d488852.png&h=258859d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd8d9c8ca99396fbf016c7dc9d4fd50b7e4ac023","tid":537894,"uid":43825,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:08:54.000Z","msg":"一開頭我記得係10蚊度<br />\n之後不斷加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8000524d174bacb2ec8cb741f4ebe36da88c5ce","tid":537894,"uid":69013,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:15:11.000Z","msg":"台式連鎖飲品2005年後開始愈來愈多，頭果批應該15蚊左右700cc。 <br />\n2005年前後台式餐廳入面既珍珠奶茶單買普遍要20+，跟餐10-15蚊。<br />\n如果講緊小食店沖出來果d, 5-10蚊都有，不過味道質素參差不齊。<br />\n<br />\n呢幾年台式飲品舖都偏向「精品」化同愈來愈貴，平均價由15蚊升到20蚊左右。"},{"pid":"c6aaf195c612e6bb3e4398f2c4828f30b8d1ff36","tid":537894,"uid":40716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9cd09c88ba9b81437da158e106fc13b79820a096","tid":537894,"uid":34489,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ca27269789327c2e2c164e41e3a2cb5781432779","tid":537894,"uid":3742,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T13:58:09.000Z","msg":"好飲30蚊都比得過<br />\n最弊難飲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T14:00:38.000Z","msg":"但係講緊好多台式飲品專門店都係D垃圾粉溝出黎<br />\n同D10蚊8蚊杯一樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:17:41.000Z","msg":"例如邊幾間？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93029fbed7f29559f054eefb51f518af69c5986","tid":537894,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:20:43.000Z","msg":"我1889年個陣1蚊杯"},{"pid":"a289bc4643acc05598ec175f45a7f3d97391d644","tid":537894,"uid":157277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:21:18.000Z","msg":"4,5蚊幾耐之前？"},{"pid":"b148f16eb15a4c699192430891a605988493ab92","tid":537894,"uid":114139,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:32:15.000Z","msg":"我記得一出果陣，大概90年代尾係賣緊差唔多十蚊杯，有啲豆花嘅係十幾，你4，5蚊果啲係咪大陸買呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afa8a051c88a0c0125128c63ac9c76414bc86cf1","tid":537894,"uid":55125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:39:21.000Z","msg":"我一直覺得呢d野好撚貴 <br />\n但d人又捨得飲"},{"pid":"11baa243c67f164ad25c8a88c7141797e8848cfb","tid":537894,"uid":24775,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:44:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個淨係識仙跡岩，但要成廿蚊杯勁貴<br />\n有好少量既茶記都有得飲，不過都要加十蚊八蚊<br />\n一年都唔知飲唔飲到5杯<br />\n仲記得以前d搖茶機好嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係 細個飲仙跡岩多 個陣覺得好好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04748b6323adf37f6dcc0ed4cda209a1e5c3df58","tid":537894,"uid":93436,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:49:13.000Z","msg":"細個仙跡岩一家三口share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好貴 差唔多13-15年前<br />\n到8-10年前$12杯貢茶 叫好抵飲"},{"pid":"84cd60e38b2fb12f5b0aded0066c85a8e89db61e","tid":537894,"uid":92856,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:52:03.000Z","msg":"一開頭熱嘅單買都8-12蚊，凍嘅好似大杯啲所以14-16<br />\n<br />\n而家貴多數因為租啦仲駛問&hellip;乜叉都炒貴哂。想食平又正嘅唔太易<br />\n<br />\n樓主講4-5可能真係大陸。香港好難去到咁平"},{"pid":"578166d742fc1e3b9929d3a89ec46b127fa4e991","tid":537894,"uid":2020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T17:12:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個仙跡岩一家三口share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好貴 差唔多13-15年前<br />\n到8-10年前$12杯貢茶 叫好抵飲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飲過而家果d就知貢茶係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當年貢茶好hit 開到四圍都係<br />\n之後開始多台飲店黎港"},{"pid":"edef914b18efbec9f7e690b3af98d43e4cecc148","tid":537894,"uid":164714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T17:18:04.000Z","msg":"好多年前日出茶太12蚊"},{"pid":"3c47312b027dcf5f4e560afdeb6bc8fe55d85ae3","tid":537894,"uid":11418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T18:11:20.000Z","msg":"題外話，好記得好多年之前(起碼十幾年)香港流行飲咩沙冰，成條旺角都有賣。賣賣下又消失曬"},{"pid":"cb0265b736439f58761ba1e7bf5ce40043284c2c","tid":537894,"uid":59830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T18:22:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d7b8293d4ba81c1af3a0dd90d75350a8c9c0aa9","tid":537894,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T19:02:21.000Z","msg":"天水圍新北江，元朗十年前真係四五蚊杯！<br />\n仲有搞肚痛機沙冰都係三四蚊杯！"},{"pid":"ab35a4e670d65fb75cae8c6f2a5dba83124a9bef","tid":537894,"uid":48483,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T20:04:17.000Z","msg":"02-03年mk唔係有間水世界/冰世界$3-4杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就'台式'$7-10杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過呢到多小學雞未必知係咩黎"},{"pid":"4155499ae500c25f014a11000de234ad31c4042d","tid":537894,"uid":378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1130e9091a88739d6b18234371d9bef0f9a17bd9","tid":537894,"uid":147499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T14:55:08.000Z","msg":"有冇人記得以前旺角有間叫台式既小食鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n賣好大粒既牛丸同四寶丸<br />\n佢d布甸奶茶係布甸多過奶茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇住佢由6蚊加到12蚊<br />\n最後冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T21:06:04.000Z","msg":"我都好掛住呢間野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係旺電旁邊既<br />\n有無人知間野係咪轉左地方？？"},{"pid":"1b3c004e97aebf5679131b2f51a9f962d3dd2241","tid":537894,"uid":83303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T21:21:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台式連鎖飲品2005年後開始愈來愈多，頭果批應該15蚊左右700cc。 <br />\n2005年前後台式餐廳入面既珍珠奶茶單買普遍要20+，跟餐10-15蚊。<br />\n如果講緊小食店沖出來果d, 5-10蚊都有，不過味道質素參差不齊。<br />\n<br />\n呢幾年台式飲品舖都偏向<span style=\"color: red;\">「精品」</span>化同愈來愈貴，平均價由15蚊升到20蚊左右。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n珍珠奶茶精品咗都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又貴又肥又多糖 仲要九成都好難飲<br />\n所謂最好飲個間天仁茗茶近依一兩年都勁唔掂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c241a701b4d8948b148cbc2db4946334683480","tid":537894,"uid":12536,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T21:40:35.000Z","msg":"屯門置樂有 6-7蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864dddd640c6a12a600d3f2abbb7c3560448eedd","tid":537894,"uid":86585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T10:09:19.000Z","msg":"喺香港乜撚都貴架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc201e62467bbe1dda6e578c157236b9fadbc639","tid":537894,"uid":33357,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"63ee5e403d3978ad1b8d0680fae144ed7f2cb13b","tid":537894,"uid":33357,"like":4,"dislike":34,"score":-30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T09:27:17.000Z","msg":"可能宜家材料著重健康d? <br />\n用鮮奶 禁用反式脂肪既野 <br />\n無咁化學"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T12:01:26.000Z","msg":"痴撚線講事實都咁多負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n街市 街邊檔6-12蚊杯果d你飲埋我果份[<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9baab63bcddf8c4396ac4e2c37e99a324d62721","tid":537894,"uid":13460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T14:06:00.000Z","msg":"天仁茗茶珍珠奶綠有無得自己整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}